---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const faqs = [
  {
    q: "What happens after I place an order?",
    a: `Within <strong>2 days</strong> of your order I'll reach out by email to confirm all the details — your photo, size, style choice, and any notes you left me. This is also a good moment to add anything you forgot.<br><br>
Once your vase is finished (usually <strong>2–3 weeks</strong> from confirmation), I'll email you photos of the finished piece for your <strong>final approval</strong>.<br><br>
If you love it — brilliant! We'll sort out shipping together at that point.<br><br>
If it's not quite right and you'd rather not go ahead, I'll issue a <strong>70% refund</strong> — the remaining 30% covers materials and studio time for the made-to-order piece. The whole point is that you end up with something you adore.`,
    accent: "var(--blush-soft)",
  },
  {
    q: "What should I write in the notes?",
    a: `The notes field is the most important part of your order — the more you give me, the more of <em>them</em> ends up in the vase.<br><br>
Good things to mention:<br>
<ul>
  <li>Their name (even pet names / nicknames)</li>
  <li>Colours they love, or a favourite item of clothing</li>
  <li>Distinctive features — a birthmark, a crooked tooth, one floppy ear, freckles</li>
  <li>Their personality in a word or two (chaotic, gentle, always-smiling…)</li>
  <li>Any style details you'd like me to lean into or avoid</li>
</ul>
A great photo plus a handful of sentences means I can make something that <em>really</em> looks like them. A photo alone is a good start, but the notes are where the magic happens.`,
    accent: "#cfe6e2",
  },
  {
    q: "What are the sizes?",
    a: `All vases are bud vases — perfect for a single wildflower or a small stem.<br><br>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Size</th><th>Height</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td>Small</td><td>~7 cm</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Medium</td><td>~12 cm</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Large</td><td>~20 cm</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<br>
Because every piece is hand-built on the wheel, each vase may vary by <strong>±2 cm</strong> — that's part of the handmade charm, not a defect.`,
    accent: "#fbe6b0",
  },
  {
    q: "Can I send the photo later?",
    a: `Yes — you can place your order without a photo and send it to me afterwards. Just drop it in the confirmation email I'll send within 2 days, or use the <a href="/contact">contact form</a>. I won't start making your vase until I have a photo I'm happy working from.`,
    accent: "var(--blush-soft)",
  },
  {
    q: "Do you ship worldwide?",
    a: `Shipping is arranged <strong>after</strong> you've approved the finished vase — so you're not paying for delivery upfront. Once you've given the thumbs up, I'll give you shipping options and costs based on where you are. I pack everything carefully; these little folks travel well.`,
    accent: "#cfe6e2",
  },
  {
    q: "How long does it take?",
    a: `From the moment you confirm your order details, expect around <strong>2–3 weeks</strong> to completion. I'll reach out within 2 days of your order to kick things off, and I'll keep you posted if anything changes.`,
    accent: "#fbe6b0",
  },
];
---

<Layout
  title="FAQ — Flowerenco"
  description="Everything you need to know about ordering a custom hand-made character vase from Flowerenco — the process, sizes, notes, and what happens after you buy."
>
  <section class="wrap faq-page">
    <div class="faq-intro">
      <span class="pill" style="background: var(--sage)">good questions</span>
      <h1>FAQ</h1>
      <p class="sub">Everything you need to know before (and after) you order.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-list">
      {faqs.map((item) => (
        <details class="faq-item card" style={`--accent: ${item.accent}`}>
          <summary class="faq-q">
            <span>{item.q}</span>
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-a" set:html={item.a} />
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="faq-cta card">
      <p>Still have a question?</p>
      <a class="btn tomato" href="/contact">Message the studio</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .faq-page { padding: 2rem 0 3rem; max-width: 760px; }

    .faq-intro { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .faq-intro h1 { font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem); margin: 0.6rem 0 0.3rem; }
    .faq-intro .sub { color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 1.1rem; margin: 0; }

    .faq-list { display: grid; gap: 0.9rem; }

    .faq-item {
      border-radius: var(--radius) !important;
      overflow: visible !important;
      transition: box-shadow 0.15s;
    }
    .faq-item[open] {
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(52,48,43,0.14);
    }
    .faq-item[open] .faq-q {
      background: var(--accent);
      border-bottom: var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius) var(--radius) 0 0;
    }

    .faq-q {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1.1rem 1.4rem;
      font-family: "Fredoka", sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      list-style: none;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      transition: background 0.12s;
      user-select: none;
    }
    .faq-q::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    .faq-q:hover { background: var(--accent); }

    .faq-icon {
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      width: 26px; height: 26px;
      border: 2.5px solid var(--ink);
      border-radius: 50%;
      position: relative;
    }
    .faq-icon::before,
    .faq-icon::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      background: var(--ink);
      border-radius: 2px;
      top: 50%; left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    }
    .faq-icon::before { width: 10px; height: 2.5px; }
    .faq-icon::after { width: 2.5px; height: 10px; transition: transform 0.2s; }
    details[open] .faq-icon::after { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(90deg); }

    .faq-a {
      padding: 1.2rem 1.4rem 1.4rem;
      color: var(--ink-soft);
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .faq-a :global(strong) { color: var(--ink); }
    .faq-a :global(a) { color: var(--cobalt); font-weight: 700; }
    .faq-a :global(ul) { margin: 0.5rem 0; padding-left: 1.3rem; display: grid; gap: 0.25rem; }
    .faq-a :global(table) { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; max-width: 320px; }
    .faq-a :global(th),
    .faq-a :global(td) { text-align: left; padding: 0.45rem 0.9rem; border: 2px solid var(--ink); }
    .faq-a :global(thead tr) { background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); font-family: "Fredoka", sans-serif; }
    .faq-a :global(tbody tr:nth-child(even)) { background: #f5f0e8; }

    .faq-cta {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding: 1.6rem 1.8rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .faq-cta p {
      font-family: "Fredoka", sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin: 0;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
